<h2 id="card-sorting">Card Sorting</h2>
<p>A simple workshop to ideate all the possibilities with the stakeholders. Itâ€™s important in brainstorming to allow everyone to produce ideas without judgment at this stage. Participants are encouraged to throw any idea out there. Even something that seems like a bad idea may spark a good idea in someone else. After we have collected an  list of ideas, I sorted them accordingly.</p>

